730059E6.Line1.BAE4.Bar: Snake bites. At least he died with a blade in his hand.

7300649C.Line1.BAE4.Dru: Snake venom. The poor child died quickly.

73008D67.Line1.BAE4.Nec: The body is cold and covered in snake bites. It has lain here a while.

73009FB9.Line1.BAE4.Rog: Snakes. At least he took a few of the bastards with him. Good lad.

7300A405.Line1.BAE4.Sor: The snakes must have attacked in great numbers. Poor child.
